00:49:39.586 --> 00:49:42.030 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: OK.

00:49:42.030 --> 00:49:45.320 align:middle line:84%
A few years later, after the
Invisible Garment work came in,

00:49:45.320 --> 00:49:48.180 align:middle line:84%
I had yet another
mystical experience.

00:49:48.180 --> 00:49:54.660 align:middle line:84%
And in this case, I was shown
a series of concentric balls,

00:49:54.660 --> 00:49:57.810 align:middle line:90%
