00:49:57.810 --> 00:50:01.830 align:middle line:84%
And I could see that
within these colors

00:50:01.830 --> 00:50:04.170 align:middle line:90%
the principles were located.

00:50:04.170 --> 00:50:06.840 align:middle line:84%
So there were four principles
in each of these spheres

00:50:06.840 --> 00:50:09.000 align:middle line:90%
that I saw.

00:50:09.000 --> 00:50:11.790 align:middle line:84%
And then, they turned
around, and they--

00:50:11.790 --> 00:50:14.550 align:middle line:84%
these spheres
turned around and on

00:50:14.550 --> 00:50:17.040 align:middle line:84%
what I call the other
side of the rainbow,

00:50:17.040 --> 00:50:19.050 align:middle line:90%
there were different colors.

00:50:19.050 --> 00:50:21.150 align:middle line:90%
And the principles had moved.

00:50:21.150 --> 00:50:27.170 align:middle line:84%
So I was being shown, I felt,
that the principles participate

00:50:27.170 --> 00:50:29.450 align:middle line:84%
with each other in
a way that creates

00:50:29.450 --> 00:50:37.320 align:middle line:84%
a collective energy that
flows through our lives

00:50:37.320 --> 00:50:40.220 align:middle line:84%
but also flows through
our cultures, that

00:50:40.220 --> 00:50:43.010 align:middle line:84%
flows through our
societies, and whatever.

00:50:43.010 --> 00:50:48.470 align:middle line:84%
So you can look at the dreams
and the colors that show up

00:50:48.470 --> 00:50:52.100 align:middle line:84%
in the dreams, and those colors
will give you information

00:50:52.100 --> 00:50:54.740 align:middle line:90%
about that particular flow.

00:50:54.740 --> 00:50:56.880 align:middle line:90%
Let me get more concrete.

00:50:56.880 --> 00:51:00.350 align:middle line:84%
So let's take blue,
the color blue.

00:51:00.350 --> 00:51:03.650 align:middle line:84%
In this work that I was
taught, the way I was shown it

00:51:03.650 --> 00:51:10.370 align:middle line:84%
in this mystical download,
blue is a frequency that--

00:51:10.370 --> 00:51:11.990 align:middle line:90%
it's a metaphor for frequency.

00:51:11.990 --> 00:51:14.780 align:middle line:84%
I'm not talking about
literally your sweater.

00:51:14.780 --> 00:51:19.460 align:middle line:84%
I'm talking about blue
as a frequency that is--

00:51:19.460 --> 00:51:24.740 align:middle line:84%
it influences culture and
people in very specific,

00:51:24.740 --> 00:51:26.450 align:middle line:90%
rational thinking.

00:51:26.450 --> 00:51:29.780 align:middle line:84%
So blue is the
sphere of science.

00:51:29.780 --> 00:51:32.810 align:middle line:84%
Blue is the sphere
just give me the facts,

00:51:32.810 --> 00:51:35.570 align:middle line:90%
and I'll work with them.

00:51:35.570 --> 00:51:39.080 align:middle line:84%
Green is the sphere of
balance and harmony,

00:51:39.080 --> 00:51:41.120 align:middle line:84%
so green is the
sphere of healing

00:51:41.120 --> 00:51:45.270 align:middle line:84%
and wholeness and the new
sciences, so to speak.

00:51:45.270 --> 00:51:47.660 align:middle line:84%
On the other side
of the rainbow,

00:51:47.660 --> 00:51:51.260 align:middle line:84%
blue and green
combine to, what I

00:51:51.260 --> 00:52:00.050 align:middle line:84%
call, turquoise, that new way
of looking at healing and fact,

00:52:00.050 --> 00:52:05.480 align:middle line:84%
bringing them together to place
them in a contextual context

00:52:05.480 --> 00:52:07.070 align:middle line:84%
