level of truth.

00:52:07.070 --> 00:52:09.110 align:middle line:84%
It's a more evolved
level of truth.

00:52:09.110 --> 00:52:11.810 align:middle line:84%
The other side of the
rainbow is an evolution

00:52:11.810 --> 00:52:14.280 align:middle line:90%
from where we are now.

00:52:14.280 --> 00:52:19.820 align:middle line:84%
So if you take the principle
purity, which is in blue,

00:52:19.820 --> 00:52:23.210 align:middle line:84%
