that you are perceiving,

00:52:37.640 --> 00:52:42.500 align:middle line:84%
or that you did perceive,
something about that logos,

00:52:42.500 --> 00:52:47.300 align:middle line:84%
that healed thought, pure
thought word turquoise energy.

00:52:47.300 --> 00:52:48.230 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Interesting.

00:52:48.230 --> 00:52:48.850 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: Does that
